Build and installation instructions for pyscannerbit 
(Python interface to ScannerBit)

---

Let <root> be the main GAMBIT root directory.
cd <root>/build
cmake ..
make ScannerBitCAPI

This will build the C API for ScannerBit into a shared library

cd <root>/contrib/pyscannerbit
python setup.py install

This will build and install pyscannerbit (which is a python wrapper of the ScannerBit C API)

